accessibility.text: my role
lct-sketch.jpeg
Design an engaging, modern layout for the brand’s redesign of their website
Adapt brand’s guidelines for print media into a cohesive visual language for digital communications
Implement design patterns from approved concepts into reusable CSS components
pasted-image.png
Determine client’s wants from provided sketches and information
Create wireframes of page layouts, seeking client’s feedback and approval before advancing concept
Build visual identity using existing branding documents as guideline, produce prototypes of key pages
With approval of design concept, write and test CSS components for site
